Hello everyone!

I have been trying to successfully run the ElevatorSimulation and the SimpleDifferentialDrive Example Java projects to no avail.

With the Elevator simulation, as shown in the below image, the elevator height jitters around 0.
With the drive simulation, once I use the joystick, the gyro reading becomes unstable and the simulation robot drives in circles.

Have the Simulation Code Examples been successfully run by anybody?

Thanks for your time!
